{"tid":1610392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(長文) 我地要照顧「英雄榜」嘅人一世！一世當佢地係英雄！","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T19:14:41.000Z","uid":2719,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0b24a9c881900e2577b536fc70708181d8f752ed","tid":1610392,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"點解黑警完全唔撚驚後果？除咗上司力撐，仲有就係就算坐監，狗隊都會聚籌安家費，夠買樓又剩咁。點解抗爭者咁淆被補？因為一輸就乜都無！<br />\n<br />\n其實，我地可以令「英雄」無後顧之憂！例如巨額安家費、一世追捧、搵工一條龍等名利都俾曬佢地。當你知道有咁好「福利」，你仲怕唔怕做「英雄」？<br />\n<br />\n我地依家只有「怒氣」，「士氣」真係無乜，次次有無數手足受傷同被捕，次之都輸有乜士氣可言？如果我地知道有「英雄」得到佢應有嘅回報，用金錢黎回報佢地，即時鼓勵埋其他抗爭者！<br />\n<br />\n我知道岳英雄拍片講過唔洗捐錢俾佢，但你話我口臭都好，現實依家睇佢一定衰緊，我地唔撚理架啦，佢一出事就一定要求佢俾銀行戶口我地捐錢！<br />\n<br />\n你要義士出聲叫你地捐，感覺上出黎好似為錢咁，義士一定唔會咁做。但如果係我地逼鳩佢求下你俾我地幫你啦之類，係我地逼鳩佢一定要收我地錢，為佢地，做到咁柒都要求，等佢地有錢收有台階下，乖乖地收我地嘅錢，令全香港義士都知，為香港付出，你最多失去自由，但其他你會得到更多！<br />\n<br />\n你都只係十幾歲/廿幾歲/俾你坐10年好未！你都未夠40！你就有一層樓！你坐緊嗰時，你家人就個個月收租，唔洗擔心啊！<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩寧願唔好坐，我夠知，但出得黎革命就預咗實有人坐，講野踏實同現實少少，我地要令坐嘅義士除失去自由外，得到更多！"},{"pid":"7bd3ae340fea1a9e908d5232f325c0b708b98f9d","tid":1610392,"uid":258291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:22:36.000Z","msg":"贊成"},{"pid":"a49eee91579869e063a044e2cb7d8da62ef51529","tid":1610392,"uid":328026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"比人當condom既感覺好難受，唔可以令佢地覺得比人忘記。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ccf94b3681edbd3ebab99998fac82849f1cee3","tid":1610392,"uid":2719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"得兩個P牌幫我推，大家咪當義士係CONDOM啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fb9c92344370587464934fd9aef6e62ffa8b6f","tid":1610392,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13c85ef11253037c26b4b6a26d88de13b8be7e30","tid":1610392,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae9d5d101b98abed6c170026ea78bd0c1d1bbf0","tid":1610392,"uid":242184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"b1516cf3b74afc58bdfd6015c9bf7d1afd086a22","tid":1610392,"uid":205378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:30:21.000Z","msg":"【長文】✰✰ 一個港島街坊有野想同今日港島班前線講 ✰✰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610354</a>"},{"pid":"4d30d68a3f7a5856e5fea668e1592ff986eed2d1","tid":1610392,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街"},{"pid":"34be01c8c5da0a176903f3cb68832634a0d32fe9","tid":1610392,"uid":161333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:30:59.000Z","msg":"推 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7c1d2f1bf9f468bdb64ba9cf3bd441e02f6acf","tid":1610392,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:33:25.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"817b0f26c740ddc19812db3500447fff03558b34","tid":1610392,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"0c673cefee624cbeee4dae52219a100023b448a1","tid":1610392,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"支持!!!! 我想出錢可以點"},{"pid":"bce4556369f6df29d10d1b7aa1391ad6e5bb8af3","tid":1610392,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:51:32.000Z","msg":"推 有錢出錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眾籌開鋪頭請義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6a6742a498270399cb7d92b1590813e86f3427","tid"